text: Bruno Goyens de Heusch (born 15 March 1959) is a Belgian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Belgium Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ixelles
